{"type": "article", "id": 26266, "title": "做个冰，也要让生活更有趣一些｜这个设计了不起", "description": "每个周末，《好奇心日报》都会找个主题为你寻找精彩设计。", "date": "2016-05-01T07:06:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 4927, "name": "冰格"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 21, "praise_count": 960, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021559359Mi3zlFmQVB0KLUS.jpg", "contents": "\r\n\r\n<p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p>\r\n<p class=\"\">夏天将至，吃冰、喝冰饮是件畅快事儿。想要为其再添些乐趣，不妨关注我们本周推荐的这几款好物。</p>\r\n<h2>Polar Ice by Monos</h2>\r\n<p>来看这款日本品牌 Monos 出品的极地冰格（Polar Ice），它是一款简单的制冰器，因为可以制作出南北极野生动物的立体冰雕感觉的冰块，显得要特别几分。早在 2009 年的东京设计周，极地冰格便已面世，但直到现在它才真正量产。极地冰格由食品级硅树脂制作而成，使用时只需把水灌入其中，盖上盖子，放进冷冻室便可，不久便能看到漂浮其中的北极熊或是南极企鹅了。</p>\r\n<p>如果你用它来喝碳酸饮料的话，不仅可以看到水上可爱的企鹅，水下则是不断上升的气泡。</p>\r\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\r\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021559130HOg9lk7ovUrGZN4.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.54\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702155914Nnu2gv3XHIfCjth4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.59491525\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702155915ogrM4vEWCapFhVXq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702155915gfBEzyebPinwoj8r.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.54545455\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021559161Vc0HqDOyhbwlagi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.638\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702155916VQo1shvlp6ILaMEB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69350649\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Whiskey Wedge by UncommonGoods</h2>\r\n<p>这个推荐送给好酒之人。如果你滴酒不沾，冻奶茶、冰可乐之类的总会喝的吧，也用得到。喜欢喝冰酒、冻奶茶、冰可乐的人不在少数，但却总是因为冰块的融化而影响了饮品本身的味道，就拿酒来说，酒味减淡总是件扫兴的事。美国卖创意设计产品的网站 UncommonGoods 上有一款创意冰格 Whiskey Wedge，用它喝酒的好处在于，你只需将它放入酒杯，然后灌入水，水将依冰格的形状冷冻凝结为一个斜坡状的冰块，而且能与酒隔开，保证酒的原始味道，还能享受冰镇的口感。售价 116.29 元，<a href=\"http://www.uncommongoods.com/product/whiskey-wedge#rd?sukey=fa67fe3435f5c4beefa03373a96d6ad6ff4f65bac4b60161b834c345c332068628e306d5894449ff3c5e73ff70e47a05\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p>\r\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\r\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702155917G0dOyI9r8thfTLXx.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021559172qOmnXPFphbkJxds.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702155918Y0IABm5JpO7v2Re6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.85925926\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702155918oMaAV4hPuXSKgQwt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>VÉRTICE by Matheus Pinto, Gustavo Billo, Henrique Dallmeyer,Fernanda Filippin, Bruna Dipp, Guilherme Camejo, Artur Migotto, Nathália Braga</h2>\r\n<p>夏天在家里开派对，VÉRTICE 简直是款必备神器，且颜值极高。光是看其如好似切割过的钻石的外观，就给人一种很高级的感觉，优雅中还带着一丝清凉气息。而这个如钻石一般的形状，并不是只为好看，设计团队还考虑到了冰块的最大接触面积，以便于节约空间。多面的设计可以减少底部承重，将重量分散至各个切割面。底部 170° 斜面的设计也更方便酒瓶的拿取。</p>\r\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\r\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702155919mNzvElZRs0pk62HM.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702155920aO8YqVz5U6wpLF4J.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021559217Zg1mcevoUKSO4XB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702155921DlWpQydcTvMUh1Gq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021559214UaylJAZF3WYfrm0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702155922N7IcbOpaosX9CVLj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>PINEAPPLE ICE TRAYS </h2>\r\n<p>冰格设计中较为常见的做法是设计一些可爱的模具，比如机器猫、象棋、钻石。而这款菠萝形状的冰块则可以印上 12 块小的冰菠萝，每一块都带有交叉纹路，形成自然的深浅变化，就像一个个小的冰雕。硅胶做的模具有多种颜色选择，售价 17 美元，<a href=\"http://www.shoppigment.com/collections/the-bar/products/blazing-yellow-hot-coral-pineapple-ice-trays-set-2?utm_campaign=Pinterest%20Buy%20Button&amp;utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=Pinterest&amp;utm_content=pinterest-buy-button-0988127d1-08d8-455a-9383-fd79996c526f\" rel=\"nofollow\">这里是购买链接</a>。</p>\r\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\r\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702155923BsQEj2kpAfzVMdFT.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.50117647\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021559238lFESvmnLcJiYrto.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0712963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702155924XCutx6LP2jem8WdV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.79722222\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702155924cKPY6tdlCyGRuFEf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6787037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>FreezTHAT! byTHAT! Inventions</h2>\r\n<p class=\"\">这是美国的团队 THAT! 设计的速冻盒，它有一个类似雪花的结构。每一个小的格子都是一个三角体，可以在 10 分钟内结成冰块并快速融化，非常实用。它甚至可以速冻巧克力、水果、咖啡，引起人们制作甜品的欲望。产品刚刚完成<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/that/freezthat-frozen-treats-in-a-flash/description\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹</a>，单个售价 18 美元，预计今年上市。<br></p>\r\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\r\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702155925J3Y0HKwyzUVb4jSg.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702155926xD6vYd04FuNaPsnG.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.525\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702155926gLfzrPy5jV0QUuCq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702155927IkUVvdgNa82Q7Ysq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56323529\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702155927s4G9yR6zSBXTrtcq.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Frozen Peas by Alessandro Martorelli for Suck UK</h2>\r\n<p class=\"\">这款豌豆荚的冰格算是冰格设计中最经典的一种，它也是用硅胶做的。从缝隙中装进水后冻住三到五个球形冰块，通过挤压将冰块掉进水杯中，就像剥豌豆一样。球形冰块的溶解速度要慢于方形冰块，而这种有互动的设计也增加了生活的趣味。此外，它还有方便旅行时携带的特征。售价 10 英镑，可以英国电商网站&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.suck.uk.com/products/frozen-peas/#info\" rel=\"nofollow\">Suck UK</a>&nbsp;上购买。<br></p>\r\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\r\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702155929lA9BFh7iRzgyQasn.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702155932ELHBw8bgGdQ7UJ5p.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702155933wy7XouksFzcZ1K4j.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.4375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702155934DCQgvKFWi4xMycdJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702155935jQbqnXJ5x8eo7SKH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.42730496\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.uncommongoods.com/product/whiskey-wedge#rd?sukey=fa67fe3435f5c4beefa03373a96d6ad6ff4f65bac4b60161b834c345c332068628e306d5894449ff3c5e73ff70e47a05\" rel=\"nofollow\">UncommonGoods</a>、<a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/2048769/VERTICE\" rel=\"nofollow\">Behance</a></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n"}